#. Tag: title
#: mount.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "MountMan: work with your mounted file systems"
msgstr "MountMan: delajte z nameščenimi datotečnimi sistemi"

#. Tag: primary
#: mount.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mount"
msgstr "Montiraj"

#. Tag: para
#: mount.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"MountMan is a tool which helps you manage your mounted file systems. Once "
"invoked, it displays a list of every mounted file system. For each file "
"system, MountMan displays its name (which is the actual device name - &ie; "
"<filename class=\"directory\">/dev/sda1</filename> for a first partition on "
"first <hardware>HDD</hardware>), its type (ext4, ext3, ntfs, vfat, "
"ReiserFS...) and its mount point on your system (the folder on which the "
"file system is mounted)."
msgstr ""
"MountMan je orodje, ki vam pomaga upravljati nameščene datotečne sisteme. Ko "
"je priklican, prikaže seznam vseh nameščenih datotečnih sistemov. Za vsak "
"datotečni sistem MountMan prikaže njegovo ime (ki je dejansko ime naprave - "
"&ie; <filename class=\"directory\">/dev/sda1</filename> za prvo particijo na "
"prvem <hardware>HDD</hardware>) , njegov tip (ext4, ext3, ntfs, vfat, "
"ReiserFS...) in njegovo točko namestitve v vašem sistemu (mapa, v kateri je "
"nameščen datotečni sistem)."

#. Tag: para
#: mount.docbook:19
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want filter out non-removable devices from the list, just check the "
"item <guilabel>Show only removable devices</guilabel> at the left of the "
"device list."
msgstr ""
"Če želite s seznama filtrirati neodstranljive naprave, preprosto označite "
"element <guilabel>Prikaži samo odstranljive naprave</guilabel> na levi "
"strani seznama naprav."

#. Tag: title
#: mount.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>MountMan</title>"
msgstr "<title>MountMan</title>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: mount.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>MountMan</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>MountMan</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: mount.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"MountMan also displays usage information using total size, free size, and "
"percentage of available space free. If those numbers say <guilabel>N/A</"
"guilabel>, that usually means that the file system is not mounted. Left "
"clicking on a file system displays a pie chart on the left of the window, "
"graphically displaying the usage information for the file system. Clicking "
"on a non-mounted file system will display <guilabel>not mounted</guilabel> "
"instead of the graph."
msgstr ""
"MountMan prikaže tudi informacije o uporabi glede na skupno velikost, prosto "
"velikost in odstotek razpoložljivega prostega prostora. Če te številke "
"pravijo <guilabel>N/A</guilabel>, to običajno pomeni, da datotečni sistem ni "
"nameščen. Levi klik na datotečni sistem prikaže tortni grafikon na levi "
"strani okna, ki grafično prikazuje informacije o uporabi datotečnega "
"sistema. Če kliknete na nevpet datotečni sistem, bo namesto grafa prikazan "
"<guilabel>ni vpet</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: mount.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycap>Double-clicking</keycap> on a file system will close MountMan and "
"open that file system inside &krusader;'s active panel."
msgstr ""
"<keycap>Dvojni klik</keycap> na datotečni sistem bo zaprl MountMan in odprl "
"ta datotečni sistem v aktivni plošči &krusader;."

#. Tag: para
#: mount.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycap>Right-clicking</keycap> on a file system will open a small menu "
"which displays what actions can be performed on that file system. At the "
"moment, you can only mount, unmount and eject (if clicking on a removable "
"file system, &eg;, a &CD-ROM;)."
msgstr ""
"<keycap>Z desnim klikom</keycap> na datotečnem sistemu se odpre majhen meni, "
"ki prikazuje dejanja, ki jih je mogoče izvesti v tem datotečnem sistemu. "
"Trenutno lahko samo priklopite, odklopite in izvržete (če kliknete na "
"odstranljiv datotečni sistem, &eg; &CD-ROM;)."

#. Tag: para
#: mount.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"We plan to expand MountMan in the next evolution of &krusader;. It will be "
"able to format partitions, edit <filename>/etc/fstab</filename>, create new "
"file systems and more.... By the way, we have started working on it, see "
"<quote>Quickmode for MountMan</quote>."
msgstr ""
"MountMan nameravamo razširiti v naslednji evoluciji &krusader;. Lahko bo "
"formatiral particije, urejal <filename>/etc/fstab</filename>, ustvarjal nove "
"datotečne sisteme in več... Mimogrede, začeli smo delati na tem, glejte "
"<quote>Quickmode for MountMan</quote>."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: mount.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quickmode for MountMan"
msgstr "Quickmode za MountMan"

#. Tag: para
#: mount.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To activate Quickmode for MountMan, click lateral button with arrow on the "
"MountMan button on the <link linkend=\"mainwindow\">Main Toolbar</link>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite aktivirati Quickmode za MountMan, kliknite stranski gumb s puščico "
"na gumbu MountMan v <link linkend=\"mainwindow\">glavni orodni vrstici</"
"link>."

#. Tag: para
#: mount.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"General idea: display a list of all possible mount points. Each time the "
"menu is displayed, it determines if a mount point is mounted or not and "
"associates the correct action (mount or umount). This offers a quick "
"interface to MountMan. It is working, and currently uses KMountMan::mount "
"and unmount. It uses the new &kf5-full; services for fstab-reading and this "
"will enable us to remove a lot of code from the <quote>old</quote> MountMan."
msgstr ""
"Splošna ideja: prikaz seznama vseh možnih točk priklopa. Vsakič, ko je meni "
"prikazan, ugotovi, ali je točka vpetja vpeta ali ne, in poveže pravilno "
"dejanje (vklop ali vklop). To ponuja hiter vmesnik za MountMan. Deluje in "
"trenutno uporablja KMountMan::mount in unmount. Uporablja novi &kf5-full; "
"storitve za branje fstab in to nam bo omogočilo, da odstranimo veliko kode "
"iz <quote>starega</quote> MountMana."
